title: Valenta - Spy-Fy Privacy Case Black with Camera Covers Front & Rear for iPhone 13
description:
From the bedroom to the bathroom, our smartphones travels with us wherever we go. Thanks to the built-in Ultra wide-angle cameras with automatic night mode on the front and rear of our iPhone, a large part of our lives is captured without us even noticing. Take back control of your privacy with Valenta's Spy Fy privacy cover, because you can close the camera on the rear and your front selfie camera. This will limit any fear, but also optimally protect your cameras against damage and scratches. 
 
Key Selling Points 
 
  Simple camera sliding system front and rear 
  6 Foot drop proof 
  Integrated honeycomb system 
  TPU housing 
  Raised edges on the sides 
  Gunsmoke-colored details like buttons 
  Inside camera slide: Micro fiber 
  Matt Black color 
  Privacy print inside 
  Supports wireless charging 
  Dutch design 
  The simple camera sliding system on the front and rear prevents someone from peering through your cameras and gives back control of your privacy. 
  Use your iPhone as you always do. The Privacy Case's sliding system doesn’t hinder the use of your iPhone 11. Face ID can still be used and the slide on the back has an opening for your flashlight! 
  The raised edges on the sides and the integrated honeycomb system provide military-grade protection for your iPhone against drops and bumps. 
  The inside of the camera cover on the back is made of soft micro fibre and is resistant to scratches on the camera lens. Flexible TPU is used for the selfie camera slide on the front, which also prevents scratches on the camera lens. 
  The flexible TPU housing provides the ideal fit and honors the design of the iPhone. 
  Minimalistic, sleek and simple; The smart Dutch design proves that functionality doesn't have to be sacrificed for style. The discreet camera protections focus on what is really important and essential, Control of your Privacy! 
  Protect your iPhone and your privacy with the iPhone Privacy Case from Valenta & Spy-Fy.
product_type: Accessories & Gadgets, Brands, Consumer Electronics, Valenta

  Made with more than 50% recycled plastic 
  Updated slimmer design, same rugged protection and drop performance 
  Multi-layer defense with a solid inner shell and resilient outer slipcover 
  Port covers prevent dirt, dust and lint from clogging jacks and ports 
  Screenless design provides flawless touch response

title: TRIUMPH Tournament Cornhole Set Brown
description:
This classic outdoor game transforms a tailgate or backyard barbecue into a party. The set includes two wooden game platforms measuring 35' L x 24' W x 1.5' H and eight 6' x 6' 12.5-ounce square bean bags (four red, four blue). The sturdy, compact bag toss game features a scratch-resistant melamine laminate surface. Supporting the boards are sturdy foldable wooden legs to set up and play anywhere. After playing, pack up the bean bags in the interior compartment between the two boards for easy storage. Using the convenient rope carry handles, transport the fun anywhere. 
 
  RECREATIONAL CORNHOLE BOARDS: Two 35' L x 24' W x 1.5' H portable game platforms 
  CORNHOLE BAGS INCLUDED: Includes eight 6' x 6' 12.5-ounce toss bags (4 red and 4 blue) 
  STURDY, YET COMPACT: With scratch-resistant melamine laminate surface 
  PORTABLE PLAY: Cornhole boards feature foldable wooden legs to set up and play anywhere 
  CONVENIENT CARRY: Boards lock together for easy transportation with convenient carry handle 
 
Cornhole is a classic family outdoor game.
product_type: Indoor and Outdoor Games & Sports, Triumph

Ultra-strong phone screen protector preserves your display’s sensitive touch response and vivid clarity. Resilient and flexible, Alpha Flex installs easily and conforms to the shape of your screen. Crystal coating is scratch and shatter resistant and full-coverage adhesive keeps Alpha Flex in place. 
 
Key Selling Points 
 
  Maintains flawless touch response

  Easy to install with included tools 
  Crystal coating resists fingerprints and delivers added strength 
  Conforms to display shape for a precision fit 
  Preserves the natural vibrancy and clarity of the display

title: TRIUMPH Six Player Croquet Set
description:
Enjoy hours of fun outside playing the Triumph 6-Player Croquet Set. This outdoor game requires concentration and strategy, yet it is fun and engaging for players of all ages. Players or teams compete by using a mallet to knock a ball through several wickets arranged on the playing field, scoring points for each wicket. This croquet set comes complete with everything you need including six multicolored solid wood mallets (six 7' x 1.75' heads and six 24' x 0.75' handles), six 70mm balls, nine weather-resistant coated wire wickets, two goal stakes (18' x 0.75'), and a carrying bag. The entire set fits neatly into the carrying bag for easy transportation and storage. 
 
  Recreational backyard croquet set designed for six players 
  Six multicolored 24' x 0.75' solid wood handles are built to last 
  7' x 1.75' diameter solid wood mallet heads made to withstand play 
  Set includes six 70mm balls, wire wickets, two 18' x 3/4' diameter wood stakes 
  All pieces fit in the included carrying bag for easy transportation and storage 
 
Turn your backyard into a croquet course and let the games begin!
product_type: Indoor and Outdoor Games & Sports, Triumph

title: TRIUMPH Tournament Washer Toss Brown / Grey
description:
The Triumph Tournament Washer Box makes it easy to play washers anywhere. Washer toss is the perfect game to bring to tailgates, camping, or any outdoor event. Sturdy and compact wood construction boxes lock together for easy storage and each feature convenient carry handles. Each 13.5' L x 13.5' W x 3.5' H box is felt-lined to reduce bounce and features a regulation-size PVC center target. The box exteriors are sealed with a durable laminate for protection against scuffs and scratches. This set includes six 2' diameter powder-coated steel washers (three red and three blue). 
 
  FROM THE BEACH TO THE BACKYARD: Two 13.5' L x 13.5' W x 3.5' H felt-lined washer boxes perfect for the beach or backyard. 
  ACCESSORIES INCLUDED: Set includes six 2' diameter powder-coated steel washers (three red, three blue) 
  SCRATCH-RESISTANT: Box exteriors are sealed with durable laminate for protection against scuffs and scratches 
  CONVENIENT STORAGE: Sturdy and compact wood construction boxes lock together for easy storage 
  EASY TRANSPORT: Easily transport set with convenient carry handles 
 
Washer toss is a great portable game for any cottage, park or camping trip.
product_type: Indoor and Outdoor Games & Sports, Triumph

title: AMERICAN LEGEND 9' Kirkwood Shuffleboard / Bowling
description:
A two for one, the American Legend Kirkwood 9’ LED Light Up Shuffleboard Table with Bowling combines two beloved games in one while providing a unique twist to both. The Kirkwood’s rustic wood grain finish, grey carpeted gutters and k-shaped legs accent its classic look while the LED light up rails provide a fun, arcade feel. This multi-faceted table comes ready to play for both games. It includes AC adapter to power the LED lighting, 10 bowling pins, pin setter, and surround to prevent pins from falling off of the table for bowling and eight chrome metal weighted pucks for classic shuffleboard. 
 
  LIGHTS OUT, GAME ON – The Kirkwood provides a unique twist on this pub classic with light up LED rails. 
  CLASSIC GAME; MODERN STYLE – The Kirkwood's rustic wood grain finish, black carpeted gutters and angled legs with turnbuckle accents add to its classic look. 
  2 GAMES IN 1 – Not only is this table perfect for shuffleboard, it comes with a full bonus bowling game set, giving you the option of two games in one. 
  SMOOTH GAMEPLAY – This table comes with shuffleboard powder perfect for reducing friction and providing a smooth, gliding gameplay. 
  ACCESSORIES INCLUDED – The Kirkwood comes ready to play for both games. It includes AC Adapter for LED lights, 10 bowling pins, pin setter, and surround to prevent pins from falling off of the table for bowling and eight chrome metal weighted pucks for classic shuffleboard. 
 
Shuffleboard and bowling in one table – the perfect combination for game night fun
product_type: American Legend, Indoor and Outdoor Games & Sports, Sports & Entertainment

title: AMERICAN LEGEND 84' Kirkwood Air Hockey
description:
Add some fun and flair to your home without making it look like your local arcade. The Kirkwood 84” Air Powered Hockey Table features a beautiful, rustic wood finish paired with unique k-shaped legs – giving its classic design a modern twist that will look stunning in any home. Despite the table’s stylish exterior, its dimensions provide the same authentic arcade game play you know and love. It’s inlay electronic scoring features in-game sound effects while keeping track of goals for even more excitement. The Kirkwood’s large, 110V 60HZ blower motor provides strong airflow for fast-paced game play while the built-in control panel provides quick and easy game set up. This table hockey game has everything you need to start playing, just grab the two pucks and two pushers and get ready for hours of fun. 
 
  The rustic wood finish paired with the unique k-shaped legs give the classic design a modern twist. Enjoy arcade-style air hockey on a table that looks great in any room in the house. 
  The Kirkwood’s large dimensions (84' x 48' x 32') provide authentic, arcade-style game play. 
  The Kirkwood’s inlay electronic scoring features in-game sound effects and keeps track of goals for even more excitement. 
  This large blower motor provides strong airflow for fast-paced game play. 
  The table’s built-in control panel provides quick and easy game setup so you can start playing, fast. 
 
Add a bit of competition to any evening with the American Legend AL1010W Kirkwood 84 inch air hockey table.
product_type: American Legend, Indoor and Outdoor Games & Sports

title: AMERICAN LEGEND 52' Charger Foosball Table
description:
Perfect for all ages, the American Legend Charger 52' Foosball Table features a light oak finish, ½' chrome hollow rods, and chrome cross bar support for added support. 
 
Non-slip grips are great for that power shot with your realistic players. The Charger foosball game table has an internal ball return system and solid 3.75' square legs for stability. 
 
Keep track of the score with the abacus-style scoring 
 
The table measures 53.5' L x 26' W x 34' H and the 3/16' MDF playfield resists warping. 
 
  It includes a traditional abacus bead slide scoreboard 
  The foosball has comfortable and robust black rubber handles for firm grip and added support 
  Internal ball return system 
  1/2' hollow rods with chrome finish

title: Club3D - USB-C 3.2 Gen 1 Universal Triple 4K Charging Dock 60W Adapter Black-Model CSV 1562--Contact for latest pricing and availability
description:
USB3.2 Gen1 Type-C Universal Triple 4K60Hz 60W Charging Dock 
 
The CSV-1562 is an USB3.2 Gen1 Type-C Universal Triple 4K60Hz Charging Docking Station and is DisplayLink® Certified. The Universal Charging Dock is designed to cater for your most versatile connectivity demands. The USB 3.2 Gen1 interface supports up to 5 Gbps bandwidth, which enables you to enjoy super speed data transmission between your favorite USB peripherals and allows for up to three external 4K60Hz displays simultaneously(needs DP™ Alt mode support from the source) in addition it offers a wired network connection, up to 1Gbps, as well as audio and microphone output. By adopting PowerDelivery(PD) charging technology, the upstream charging function through USB3.2 Gen1 Type-C interface, you can charge a connected cell phone/tablet/laptop. Furthermore, the added Kensington Lock option allows you to secure your dock as well. All it needs is a free USB 3.2 Gen 1 port on your Laptop or Ultrabook to connect to the Universal Triple 4K Charging Docking Station via a single USB Type-C cable. 
 
Charging: Laptops / UltraBooks / Tablets often have limited connectivity possibilities. By adopting PD Charging technology and upstream-charging function through USB Type C interface the Club3D USB Type C Charging Dock offers unique functionality. It will charge your Notebook up to 60 Watts and through the downstream port on the front you can charge your phone up to 7.5 Watt. 
Give your Ultrabook more displays Ultrabooks and notebooks are increasingly becoming more powerful and smaller in the physical form factor. With a single USB3.2 Gen 1 port available you can now drive an HDMI™ and/or Displayport™ screen simultaneously. All it needs is a free USB3.2 Gen 1 port on your Telephone, Laptop or Ultrabook to connect to the Universal Triple 4K60Hz Charging Docking Station via a single USB cable. The Docking station will provide you with unparalleled connection options for up to three 4K60Hz displays. Whether it is thru two times the DisplayPort™ connection or thru 3 times the HDMI™ ports. The setup is easy and simple to do, provided your system supports this function.
